reviewText: A great little "clip" I have shown my MANY AOD clients! Gives a good perspective on someone who MIGHT be a bit of a snake-oil salesman!

This film was quite interesting, but very brief.  It would be great to know if this type of treatment has received a positive review from the majority of people taking advantage of it. Has the price of the treatment decreased? Will insurance ever pay for it? Is it still being used?
